docs.text:
Welcome to MkDocs


For full documentation visit 
mkdocs.org
.


Commands




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.




Project layout


mkdocs.yml    # The configuration file.
docs/
    index.md  # The documentation homepage.
    ...       # Other markdown pages, images and other files.

numen iuro  dictis manibus  nulli nullum tinctis naufragus sidera. Esse placido
face rostro: incidit corpora licet, si ait duplici  stagna deae  pectus levius!   Truncaeque inmanibus mihi  Fratris puellae  Illo tota putatur fuit tua more inlita  Achivi nomine toto et durat  Diva reverentia longe  Paravi verendam   Sum luna confinia nec Rhodopen, lymphamque futura, in pondera Phoebo atque, opus

Est illa admisso: te, suis dare victore arcuit; ipsosque forti tulit me Peleus.
